Text:
Since there are 60 seeders and no comments on here yet I thought I would start.

Obviously it was very fast download (only 25 MB) so you should download and check it out for yourself... but to be honest I was not very impressed.

None of the pictures particularly impressed me and the whole set just seemed to be a random collection of 30 high quality pictures. I mean you have a 2 random nudes, 1 anime, and 1 picture of a porcupine... All that would be fine if they were all super sexy as stated, but in my opinion only a couple of them are.

Thanks nicobolso for uploading this and you should check it out for yourself.
